<div class="pagetitle">
<h2>Program Directory</h2>
</div>
<p></p>
<p>The Hawaii Department of Health functions under the leadership of the Director and Deputy Director, and includes attached offices and agencies. Most DOH programs are under one of three administrations: health resources, environmental health and behavioral health. Follow the links below to find contact information for DOH divisions, branches and programs. If you are unable to find the program you are looking for, send us a message through our <a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/contact/">contact page</a> and we will assist in routing your inquiry.</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>Main Office: Kinau Hale<br/>1250 Punchbowl Street<br/>Honolulu, Hawaii 96813<br/>Phone: (808) 586-4400</p>
<p>
</p>
<p><strong>Director</strong><br/>Director – Kenneth S. Fink, MD, MGA, MPH<br/>Phone: (808) 586-4410</p>
<p>The Director is the chief health and environmental official for the state.  He oversees the operations of the entire department and sits on a number of key boards and committees.</p>
<p>As part of his duties, the Director is the chair of the Board of Health and oversees a number of health-related agencies that are attached to the DOH for administrative purposes. These are:</p>
<blockquote>
<table style="width: 49.1472%; height: 360px;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<tbody>
<tr style="height: 24px;">
<td style="width: 76.93%; height: 24px;"><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/communications-office/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Communications Office</a></td>
<td style="width: 22.5991%; height: 24px;">(808) 586-4417</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 24px;">
<td style="width: 76.93%; height: 24px;"><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/dcab/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Disability and Communication Access Board</a></td>
<td style="width: 22.5991%; height: 24px;">(808) 586-8121</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 24px;">
<td style="width: 76.93%; height: 24px;"><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/eoa/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Executive Office on Aging</a></td>
<td style="width: 22.5991%; height: 24px;">(808) 586-0100</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 24px;">
<td style="width: 76.93%; height: 24px;"><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/ola/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Office of Language Access</a></td>
<td style="width: 22.5991%; height: 24px;">(808) 586-8730</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 24px;">
