<td style="width: 22.5991%; height: 24px;" nowrap="nowrap">(808) 587-0787</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 24px;">
<td style="width: 76.93%; height: 24px;"><a href="https://hiddcouncil.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">State Planning Council on Developmental Disabilities</a></td>
<td style="width: 22.5991%; height: 24px;">(808) 586-8100</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</blockquote>
<p>
</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/office-of-the-deputy-director-of-health/">Deputy Director</a></strong><br/>Deputy Director – Valerie M. Kato<br/>Phone: (808) 586-4412</p>
<p>The Deputy Director of Health heads the DOH administrative offices which oversee the following:</p>
<ul>
<li><a title="Office of the Deputy Director of Health" href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/office-of-the-deputy-director-of-health/#ASO">Administrative Services Office (ASO)</a></li>
<li><a title="Office of the Deputy Director of Health" href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/office-of-the-deputy-director-of-health/#HISO">Health Information Systems Office (HISO)</a></li>
<li><a title="Office of the Deputy Director of Health" href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/office-of-the-deputy-director-of-health/#HRO">Human Resources Office (HRO)</a></li>
<li><a title="Office of the Deputy Director of Health" href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/office-of-the-deputy-director-of-health/#OHSM">Office of Health Status Monitoring (OHSM)</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/opppd/main/">Office of Planning, Policy and Program Development (OPPPD)</a></li>
<li><a title="Office of the Deputy Director of Health" href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/office-of-the-deputy-director-of-health/#OAA">Office of Affirmative Action (OAA)</a></li>
<li><a title="Office of the Deputy Director of Health" href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/office-of-the-deputy-director-of-health/#DHO">District Health Offices (DHOs)</a></li>
</ul>
<p>
</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/health-resources-administration/">Health Resources Administration</a></strong></p>
<p>Deputy Director – Debbie Kim Morikawa<br/>Phone: (808) 586-4433</p>
<p>The Health Resources Administration oversees the following:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/chronic-disease/">Chronic Disease Prevention and Health Promotion Division</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/health-resources-administration/#Communicable">Communicable Disease &amp; Public Health Nursing Division</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/docd/">Disease Outbreak Control Division</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/ems/">Emergency Medical Services &amp; Injury Prevention System Branch</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/fhsd/">Family Health Services Division</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/ohca/">Office of Health Care Assurance</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/medicalcannabis/">Office of Medical Cannabis Control and Regulation</a></li>
</ul>
<p>
</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/environmental-health-administration/">Environmental Health Administration</a></strong><br/>Deputy Director – Kathleen Ho<br/>Phone: (808) 586-4424</p>
<p>The Environmental Health Administration oversees the following:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/environmental-health-administration/#CAO">Compliance Assistance Office</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/environmental-health-administration/#HEERO">Hazard Evaluation and Emergency Response Office</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/environmental-health-administration/#EPO">Environmental Planning Office</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/environmental-health-administration/#ERO">Environmental Resources Office</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/environmental-health-administration/#EMD">Environmental Management Division</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/environmental-health-administration/#EHSD">Environmental Health Services Division</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/environmental-health-administration/#SLD">State Laboratories Division</a></li>
</ul>
<p>
</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/behavioral-health-services-administration/">Behavioral Health Administration</a></strong><br/>Deputy Director – Marian Tsuji<br/>Phone: (808) 586-4416</p>
<p>The Behavioral Health Administration oversees the following:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/behavioral-health-services-administration/#ADAD">Alcohol and Drug Abuse</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/behavioral-health-services-administration/#AMHD">Adult Mental Health</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/behavioral-health-services-administration/#CAMHD">Child and Adolescent Mental Health</a></li>
<li><a href="https://health.hawaii.gov/about/program-directory/behavioral-health-services-administration/#DDD">Developmental Disabilities</a></li>
</ul>
<p>
</p>
<p></p>
